trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Threading.ThreadPriority"></xref> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta un <xref href="System.Threading.ThreadPriority"> </xref> (e il relativo valore) di un componente hardware o software di sistema stampa.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza di <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"> </xref> classe per la proprietà specificata.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPriority> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: La `attributeName` devono essere digitati esattamente come il nome di determinate <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPriority>proprietà di un oggetto di sistema di stampa, comprese le maiuscole e minuscole.</xref:System.Threading.ThreadPriority>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.PortThreadPriority%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> object must be spelled "PortThreadPriority", not "ThreadPriority" or "Portthreadpriority".
trans-unit.target: Ad esempio, il <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.PortThreadPriority%2A>proprietà di un <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer>oggetto deve essere digitato "PortThreadPriority", non "ThreadPriority" o "Portthreadpriority".</xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> </xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.PortThreadPriority%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Threading.ThreadPriority"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Il nome del <xref href="System.Threading.ThreadPriority"> </xref> proprietà che la <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"> </xref> rappresenta.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza di <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"> </xref> classe che ha il valore specificato per la proprietà specificata.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPriority> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: La `attributeName` devono essere digitati esattamente come il nome di determinate <xref:System.Threading.ThreadPriority>proprietà di un oggetto di sistema di stampa, comprese le maiuscole e minuscole.</xref:System.Threading.ThreadPriority>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.PortThreadPriority%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> object must be spelled "PortThreadPriority", not "ThreadPriority" or "Portthreadpriority".
trans-unit.target: Ad esempio, il <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.PortThreadPriority%2A>proprietà di un <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer>oggetto deve essere digitato "PortThreadPriority", non "ThreadPriority" o "Portthreadpriority".</xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> </xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.PortThreadPriority%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Threading.ThreadPriority"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Il nome del <xref href="System.Threading.ThreadPriority"> </xref> proprietà che la <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"> </xref> rappresenta.

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Il valore della proprietà che la <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"> </xref> rappresenta.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta il valore della proprietà che la <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintThreadPriorityProperty"> </xref> rappresenta.
